2007_May 19 
Alien is a Creepy claustrophobic thriller that has gone down as one of
the best films in history. It focuses around a group of people who are
told to investigate a mysterious planet. They are savaged by an alien
they bring on board, and only one (and a cat) is left alive.<br /><br />This is a very effective film.<br /><br />It paralyses your sense of fear, and entertains you at the same time.
With great acting and a very intimidating killer, Alien has gone down
as a classic.<br /><br />Although it was surpassed by its first sequel aliens, it is still an
incredibly effective thriller.<br /><br />A giant in cinema.
